'''''Together for Days''''' is a 1972 film starring [[Clifton Davis]] and [[Samuel L. Jackson]] in his film debut. 

This independent film is about a the romance between an African-American man and a Caucasian woman and the reaction of their friends and family to the mixed race relationship. 

